text: Jugon-les-Lacs - Commune nouvelle () is a commune. It is in Brittany in the Côtes-d'Armor department in northwest France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2016 and consists of the former communes of Jugon-les-Lacs (the seat) and Dolo.Arrêté préfectoral 27 November 2015 == References == Category:2016 establishments in France Category:Communes in Côtes-d'Armor
